This old rubble might contain objects from times long past. You will have to search it thoroughly to be sure.

Value.value: Many of the books are crumbling and moldy to the point where you can’t risk picking them up. A few pages are still able to be read, though the language seems to be an archaic form of Alzhedo script. The remaining text details a time called the Year of Scarlet Scourges. During a birthday celebration, a place called Ithalyr was brought under siege by a Clan Fyrson.
